snippet.title: Get Clear on Your Vision and Go After Your Goals With Amber Sears on True Grit and Grace.
snippet.description:
If you've been feeling overwhelmed, burned out, or wondering how to build new boundaries in this digital age, Amber's wisdom will be so helpful.

As a holistic business coach Amber Sears is deeply dedicated to serving her clients from all angles—Mind, body, spirit and business. She is the CEO of @Epic Self Coaching & Retreats  and the podcast host of the Soul Powered Podcast and married to someone I am sure you have heard of @AwakenWithJP 

In her 12 years of experience running her own multiple six figure business, she's learned the inner work is paramount. 

She helps her clients cultivate deep inner strength and build their businesses around their souls unique calling.

Here’s what you will learn:⁣
❤️How to get clear on your vision.
❤️How to make goals a reality
❤️The new digital age and how to create healthy boundaries 
❤️All about retreats. Are they right for you 
❤️How to prevent burnout
❤️How to better manage your time
❤️The healthy boundaries you need to see for more productivity
❤️How so many have transitioned online in the pandemic and you can too!

🎧Listen to other inspiring episodes on Apple, Spotify, Stitcher, or Google and please let me know what you think by leaving me a rating and a review on Apple.  

And reach out to me anytime and let me know if you have any show ideas at 818-214-7378
